@page "/alert"
<h2>🔔Attention!!! Citizens!🔔</h2>
<i>As the heartbeat of our democracy, your participation matters. Let’s ignite change, one vote at a time. Here’s how you can make a difference.</i>
<MudContainer>
    <MudPaper Elevation="2">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">1.Register to Vote & Stay Informed</MudText>
        @* <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2">Subtitle (Optional)</MudText> *@
        <MudList Dense="true">
            <MudListItem>
                If you haven’t already, register as a voter. Your voice counts, & this is your ticket to shaping our nation’s destiny.
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                Knowledge is power. Dive deep into party manifestos, candidate profiles, & their track records.
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                Understand the issues that matter most to you & your community.
            </MudListItem>
        </MudList>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4">2.Question Everything</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2">Don’t settle for vague promises. Ask tough questions</MudText>
        <MudList Dense="true">
            <MudListItem>
                What are their plans for education, healthcare, & employment?.
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                How will they tackle corruption & environmental challenges?
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                Are they committed to gender equality & social justice?
            </MudListItem>
        </MudList>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">3.Debunk Myths & Hold Leaders Accountable </MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle2">MPs are our representatives, not rulers. Hold them accountable</MudText>
        <MudList Dense="true">
            <MudListItem>
                Beware of misinformation. Verify facts before sharing them.Fact-check news, memes, & WhatsApp forwards. Let truth prevail.
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                Attend town halls, ask questions, & demand transparency.Track their performance & remind them of their promises.
            </MudListItem>
        </MudList>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">4.Vote Wisely & Encourage Others</MudText>
        @* <MudText Typo="subtitle2">Subtitle (Optional)</MudText> *@
        <MudList Dense=true>
            <MudListItem>
                Look beyond party symbols. Evaluate candidates based on their integrity, vision, & commitment. Vote for someone who aligns with your values & aspirations.
            </MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>
                Be a catalyst for change. Inspire friends, family, & neighbors to vote.Organize voter awareness drives & discussions.
            </MudListItem>
        </MudList>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">5.Volunteer</MudText>
        <MudList Dense=true>
            <MudListItem>Join local NGOs or community initiatives working on voter education.</MudListItem>
            <MudListItem>Be the change you wish to see.</MudListItem>
        </MudList>

    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h5">
    Remember, democracy thrives when citizens actively participate. Let’s turn the tide together.
</MudText>
<MudText Typo="Typo.h6">
    <i>
        Spread the word, share this alert, & let’s create a vibrant, accountable India! 🌟
    </i>
</MudText>
